直接已知子类:
CeilingUnit, FloorUnit, WallUnit
public abstract class UnmovableObject extends GameObject
UnmovableObject is an abstract class inheriting from GameObject. UnmovableObject does not have a velocity, acceleration,direction, and dimensions. UnmovableObject includes WallUnit, CeilingUnit and FloorUnit.
